      • getMentionedMembers

        public java.util.List<net.dv8tion.jda.core.entities.Member> getMentionedMembers()
        Description copied from class: CommandEvent
        Copied From Message.getMentionedMembers(net.dv8tion.jda.core.entities.Guild)

        Creates an immutable list of Members representing the users of CommandEvent.getMentionedUsers() in the Guild this Message was sent in.
        This is only a convenience method and will skip all users that are not in the specified Guild.
        It will provide the CommandEvent.getGuild() output Guild to CommandEvent.getMentionedMembers(net.dv8tion.jda.core.entities.Guild).

        Overrides:
        getMentionedMembers in class CommandEvent
        Returns:
        Immutable list of mentioned Members
